[SN]TITLE[SN]
Epsom Derby 2017: Race schedules and BBC radio coverage

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
The 2017 Derby Festival will take place from 2-3 June with the Derby taking place on Saturday, 3 June at 16:30 BST.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The race is run at Epsom Downs Racecourse in Surrey over a distance of one mile, four furlongs and 10 yards on the first Saturday of June each year.
Harzand, ridden by Pat Smullen, held off the challenge of favourite US Army Ranger and Idaho to win the 2016 race.
There is live radio coverage of the Derby on BBC Radio 5 live and the BBC Sport website.
